                              E P I S O D E  -1
                       Rise of the sysadmin apprentice

            Young Darth Sidious feels that his power has grown to match his

            potential. He knows his big moment is close and there is not much

            for his master to pass on to him anymore. He is almost ready to

            face his Sith master and according to the ancient teaching of the

            order absorb the sheer power of the mighty Darth Plagueis.

            Darth Plagueis has felt the disturbance in the force and expects

            his young apprentice to come for him soon and thus fulfilling

            his apprentice's true and only destiny. Plagueis hid a number of

            secrets across the galaxy knowing that only a true Sith lord can

            find them and wield them against him in an epic battle.



                    A few p̶a̶r̶s̶e̶c̶s gigabytes later...



            The most famous smugglers duo Han Solo and Chewbacca are preparing

            for their biggest stint ever and they will make sure not to allow

            anyone to sabotage it. But one should never underestimate the ever

            ambitious former smuggler and digital reseller Lando Calrissian

            who is willing to make every effort to take all the profit himself...
